# Gmail
IMAPAccount gmail
Host imap.gmail.com
Port 993
User jiro.due@gmail.com
PassCmd "pass show mutt/jiro.due@gmail.com"
TLSType IMAPS
AuthMechs LOGIN
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt

IMAPStore gmail-remote
Account gmail

MaildirStore gmail-local
Path ~/.local/share/mail/gmail/
Inbox ~/.local/share/mail/gmail/INBOX
SubFolders Verbatim

Channel gmail
Far :gmail-remote:
Near :gmail-local:
Patterns "INBOX" "[Gmail]/Sent Mail" "[Gmail]/Drafts"
Create Both
Expunge Both
SyncState *
 
# Outlook
IMAPAccount outlook
Host outlook.office365.com
Port 993
AuthMechs LOGIN
TLSType IMAPS
User massimo.balducci@outlook.it
PassCmd "pass show mutt/massimo.balducci@outlook.it"
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt

IMAPStore outlook-remote
Account outlook

MaildirStore outlook-local
Path ~/.local/share/mail/outlook/
Inbox ~/.local/share/mail/outlook/INBOX

Channel outlook
Far :outlook-remote:
Near :outlook-local:
Patterns "INBOX" "Sent" "Drafts"
Create Both
Expunge Both
SyncState *

